{"id": 2444, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对所谓的“人生赢家”都有哪些困惑？", "description": "在“猫狗双全、人生我有”的今天，还有哪些让你感到困惑的“成功标尺”？（图片来自：视觉中国 © Collection Mix: Subjects）", "record_count": 3147, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180724174208SfjNJboryceGU2uB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 294400, "content": "活成了一个二手货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615795}, {"id": 295424, "content": "就想说，就算是人生赢家，那是你自己的事，你赢了谁，每个人的目标不同，谁在和你比赛？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 294401, "content": "赢了什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405605}, {"id": 294402, "content": "人生赢家到底是为了自己还是为了别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607970}, {"id": 294403, "content": "没有困惑。欲望无止尽，人生赢家只是达到了观者当前的欲望目标。世上本无事，庸人自扰之", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367474}, {"id": 294404, "content": "事业婚姻等等 而不是成功活出自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381307}, {"id": 294405, "content": "学历 钱 美貌 等等外在的标签成了唯一标准，却没人在乎每个个体内在的，个性的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281507}, {"id": 294406, "content": "当一个人成为了人生赢家时？会不会有，或者有多少人成为了人生输家？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457673}, {"id": 298247, "content": "想干嘛的时候就干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108770}, {"id": 294408, "content": "人生赢家真的赢了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413437}, {"id": 294409, "content": "就是不求大富大贵，但也衣食无忧，可以随心所欲", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241060}, {"id": 294410, "content": "四十岁之前争取到自己想要的物质钱财，可以不养小孩，保持身体健康，想玩玩，想吃吃，想喝喝。这就是我目前能想到的人生赢家了", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153113}, {"id": 294411, "content": "同时获得欧皇与大阴阳师称号", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241060}, {"id": 294412, "content": "当你觉得你赢了，你就赢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408662}, {"id": 294668, "content": "别人拥有你渴望而不可得的，他对比你来说就是人生赢家，或者说是你的人生的赢家。输赢不都是相对的么\n\n可笑的是大部分人其实都不确切知道自己想要什么，想赢自己都办不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972474}, {"id": 294413, "content": "赢得自己的人生就是人生赢家", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410938}, {"id": 294670, "content": "实现自己的理性", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384572}, {"id": 294415, "content": "我借了的沙，熟记海的颜色！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413434}, {"id": 294417, "content": "钱钱钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 294419, "content": "什么都拿出炫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 312376}, {"id": 294931, "content": "没见过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052534}, {"id": 294420, "content": "不存在温柔体贴，善解人意的妻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411515}, {"id": 294421, "content": "到底什么是让各种社会元素可以进行加权的同度量因素?谁能回答一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374986}, {"id": 294677, "content": "能过自己想过的生活才叫赢家，我觉得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408819}, {"id": 296213, "content": "投胎技巧分享一下？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423128}, {"id": 294423, "content": "人家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413482}, {"id": 294424, "content": "大概就是钱太多花不完这种感觉吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898883}, {"id": 294427, "content": "比我强的都是人生赢家（手动脸黑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249364}, {"id": 294428, "content": "达到财务自由，拥有真正做选择的自由，过上适合自己的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364463}, {"id": 294430, "content": "达成了令人羡慕的事情的你就是人生赢家。但是那些真的是你想要的吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413508}, {"id": 294431, "content": "可以自由表达自己的意见，选择朋友圈，选择生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413524}, {"id": 294432, "content": "有钱有钱有钱吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405267}, {"id": 294434, "content": "财务自由\n人身自由\n思想自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317230}, {"id": 294435, "content": "每个人都是独立的个体，每个人都有自己的“时区”所有的得到都是失去的开始", "image": "img/option/option/20180725131738IM8lzQUO7VihjFc4.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906062}, {"id": 294436, "content": "什么是人生赢家我都不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353667}, {"id": 294438, "content": "做自己最想做的事情 成为自己最想成为的人 找到了自己真正存在于世的意义", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413527}, {"id": 294439, "content": "离这个词越来越远了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726790}, {"id": 294440, "content": "耶，明天不上班，我是人生赢家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334651}, {"id": 294441, "content": "生活小资，阅历丰富，热爱工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1401143}, {"id": 294442, "content": "内心保持童真但行事必须脱离幼稚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412411}, {"id": 295466, "content": "没有烦恼，潇洒自在，一个属于自己独一无二生活方式才是赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418089}, {"id": 294443, "content": "读书期间:985，211\n工作时:年薪百万\n个人生活:三十岁前结婚，有车有房，有二胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357067}, {"id": 295467, "content": "赢的目的是啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418115}, {"id": 294444, "content": "幸福的人都是一样的，不幸的人各有各的不幸。赢家也类似", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413564}, {"id": 294445, "content": "弥留之际回想自己的一生，没有过不去的不甘和悔恨，能够欣然离开这个世界，就是人生赢家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413559}, {"id": 294446, "content": "人生赢家一定要结婚生子吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413570}, {"id": 294448, "content": "不结婚的女人不论多么成功精神世界多么富有。在一些什么都没有的人眼中依旧一事无成。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411509}, {"id": 294450, "content": "所以一定要有对象才算人生赢家？不然就只能是汪汪汪？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054027}, {"id": 294451, "content": "人生哪有输赢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1982}, {"id": 294452, "content": "结婚，生子，还是龙凤胎……不明白标准在哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390820}]}